msgid ""
"Update Manager should open up and tell you: **\"New distribution release "
"'22.04' is available.\"**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../22.04/index.md:63 8378787f0dca49fea632754543a995c0
msgid ""
"If not you can also use `/usr/lib/ubuntu-release-upgrader/check-new-"
"release-gtk`"
